trans-unit.source: Indicates the first day of the week to use when calling date-related functions.
trans-unit.target: Angir den første dagen i uken som skal brukes når du kaller dato-relaterte funksjoner.

trans-unit.source: When you call date-related functions, you can use the following enumeration members in your code in place of the actual values.
trans-unit.target: Når du kaller dato-relaterte funksjoner, kan du bruke følgende opplisting medlemmer i koden i stedet for de faktiske verdiene.

trans-unit.source: Some date-related functions take a `DayOfWeek` argument, a `WeekOfYear` argument, or both.
trans-unit.target: Noen funksjoner for dato-relaterte tar en `DayOfWeek` argumentet, et `WeekOfYear` argumentet eller begge deler.

trans-unit.source: The `FirstDayOfWeek` enumeration specifies the valid values for the `DayOfWeek` arguments, as well as the possible return values from the functions.
trans-unit.target: Den `FirstDayOfWeek` opplisting angir gyldige verdier for den `DayOfWeek` argumenter, i tillegg til mulige returverdier fra funksjonene.

trans-unit.source: The `DayOfWeek` argument takes the `FirstDayOfWeek` enumeration members.
trans-unit.target: Den `DayOfWeek` argumentet tar det `FirstDayOfWeek` opplisting medlemmer.

trans-unit.source: Date-related functions also return `FirstDayOfWeek` values (except `System`).
trans-unit.target: Date-relaterte funksjoner også returnere `FirstDayOfWeek` verdier (bortsett fra `System`).
